\tab\tab\tab\ul\b OUR STAKEHOLDERS\ulnone\b0\par
\fs28 1\f1\rtlch\lang1037 . \ul\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 End-Users\ulnone\b0  - These are the primary individuals who will interact with and benefit from the system\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par

\pard\ltrpar\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\ul\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Families and Caregivers\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\ulnone\par
\f0\ltrch\lang1033 1.Description\b0 : Individuals who want to monitor swimmers (e.g., children, elderly family members) to ensure their safety\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Interests\b0 : Ease of use, reliability, real-time alerts, and peace of mind\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Swimming Pool Owners and Managers\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 2.Description\b0 : Owners or managers of private, community, or commercial swimming pools\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Interests\b0 : Enhanced safety measures, compliance with safety regulations, and operational efficiency\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par

\pard\ltrpar\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f0\ltrch\lang1033 2\f1\rtlch\lang1037 . \ul\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Customers \ulnone\b0 - Entities that purchase or subscribe to the system\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par

\pard\ltrpar\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\ul\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Homeowners\ulnone\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Description\b0 : Individuals looking to install the system in their private residences\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Interests\b0 : Cost-effectiveness, seamless integration with existing home systems, and user-friendly interfaces\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\ul\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Commercial Facilities\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\ulnone\b0\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Description\b0 : Businesses such as hotels, gyms, and aquatic centers that require robust safety systems\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Interests\b0 : Scalability, reliability, comprehensive support, and integration with other security systems\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par

\pard\ltrpar\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f0\ltrch\lang1033 4\f1\rtlch\lang1037 . \ul\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Development Team \ulnone  - \b0 The technical team building the system\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par

\pard\ltrpar\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Description\b0 : Responsible for coding the application, developing the user interface, and implementing functional requirements\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Interests\b0 : Clear requirements, access to necessary tools and technologies, and collaborative work environment\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Description\b0 : Develop and refine the algorithms for drowning prediction and video analysis\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Interests\b0 : Access to quality data, computational resources, and opportunities for model improvement\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\ul\b\f0\ltrch\fs44\lang1033\par

\pard\rtlpar\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qc\par

\pard\ltrpar\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qc Functional Requirements\f1\rtlch\lang1037\par

\pard\ltrpar\sa200\sl276\slmult1\ulnone\b0\f0\ltrch\fs28\lang1033 1\f1\rtlch\lang1037 . \ul\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 User Authentication\ulnone\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Registration\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\f0\ltrch\lang1033  Users can register for an account using their email address and a unique identifier (e.g., home ID or camera serial number)\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Login\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\f0\ltrch\lang1033  \b0 Users can log in to their accounts using their registered email and password\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Password Management\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\f0\ltrch\lang1033  \b0 Users can reset their passwords through a secure password recovery process\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\b\par
\b0\f0\ltrch\lang1033 2\f1\rtlch\lang1037 . \ul\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Camera Management\ulnone\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Add Camera\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\f0\ltrch\lang1033  \b0 Users can add new cameras to the system by entering details such as camera name, username, password and IP\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Edit Camera details\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\b0\f0\ltrch\lang1033  Users can edit existing camera details, including name, category.\f1\rtlch\lang1037\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Delete Camera\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Users can remove cameras from the system as needed\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Choose Camera\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Users can select a specific camera to view its live feed \f1\rtlch\lang1037\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 3. \ul Manage Categories\ulnone\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\par
\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Switch Cameras by Category\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\f0\ltrch\lang1033  Users can switch between cameras based on predefined categories (e.g., indoor pool, outdoor pool)\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033\par
Add Category: \b0 Create new categories to organize cameras (e.g., Backyard Pool, Community Pool)\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Edit Category\b0 : Modify the name or description of existing categories\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Delete Category\b0 : Remove categories that are no longer in use\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\f0\ltrch\lang1033 4\f1\rtlch\lang1037 . \ul\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 System Settings\ulnone\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Notification Settings\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Users can configure the types of notifications,volume or where they wish to receive them.\f1\rtlch\lang1037\par
\f0\ltrch\lang1033 5\f1\rtlch\lang1037 . \ul\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Live Video Streaming\ulnone\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Real-Time Streaming\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\b0\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Users can view live video feeds from selected cameras through the application interface on their computer or mobile devices\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Multi-Camera View\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\b0\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Display multiple camera feeds simultaneously on a single screen for comprehensive monitoring\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\f0\ltrch\lang1033 6\f1\rtlch\lang1037 . \ul\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Recordings and History\ulnone\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Access to Recordings\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Users can access and review recordings based on date, camera, and category\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\b\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Manage Recordings\b0\f1\rtlch\lang1037 :\f0\ltrch\lang1033 Add, edit, or delete video recordings as needed\f1\rtlch\lang1037 .\par
\f0\ltrch\fs22\lang1033\par
